column1: IF cr_l8_oh_f_d is MF 1 AND ccr_cortisol_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
IF ccr_thaldo_d is MF 2 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 2 AND ccr_sb_oh_f_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thdoc_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 1 AND ccr_b_cortol_d is MF 0 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_tha_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
